data.description: Highly desirable location, close to everything, yet tucked away for peace and quiet. This impressive 5 bed/ 4.5 bath property welcomes you home with stainless steel appliances, newer HVAC, master on the main, huge deck for entertaining and finished basement living spaces to stretch out and enjoy. Grand foyer, vaulted family room with fireplace, breakfast area and formal dining room. Great size workshop w 2 extra unfinished rooms for storage. Large back yard that backs up to greenspace for nature lovers and low maintenance mature landscaping. Loganville Schools!! Make your appt for viewing today!
